月期油及布蘭特6月期油、一半分配給7月期油，另外20%及10%分別給8月及9月期貨。<br />\n<br />\nUSO以往主要投資在近月合約。基金提交的監管文件表示，正在調整投資組合，應對異常市況，紓緩油價前所未有崩盤帶來的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n目前較遠月份到期的原油合約價格高於近月合約。<br />\n<br />\nUSO周三收市跌10.7%，報2.51美元，連續9日下跌。自從停止發行新單位後，基金價格較周二的淨資產值出現大幅溢價。"},{"pid":"c753b4a4a6b11729331d62914c447afbcc132323","tid":1985911,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />訓身</span>"},{"pid":"e201f9470ff07865df63e006567c7c999a654744","tid":1985911,"uid":354581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b9f95d4947b657fcc9fdcde74eea516662f6cc2","tid":1985911,"uid":267448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:01:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522360-20200423.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522360-20200423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6o5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=8408f2ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522360-20200423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=de240ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522360-20200423.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n唔怪得油價升,佢反而跌, 仲有冇人未放?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"未 輸緊二百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca153f05b9fcfa35183d64e5c1b8e42550ba2527","tid":1985911,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"UCO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbdb89de0f0f9b09b99f027cb7b14191b548d23","tid":1985911,"uid":219470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"UCO同3175簡直係我人生買過最老千嘅老千股"},{"pid":"7437ab73514f370d22c50b1620cd8d621b94c2